      "text": "あなたが長瀬さん？　はじめまして\n私、星見プロダクションの佐伯遙子です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you Nagase-san? Nice to meet you.\nI'm Haruko Saeki from Hoshimi Production.",
        "id": ""
