      "text": "何言ってんだ！　星見市にLizNoirが来るなんて\nそうそうないぞ！　レアチケットなんだぞ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you talking about?\nLizNoir never comes to Hoshimi City. It's a rare ticket!",
